Rating: 2
I made this last night for A New Year's Eve party at a neighbor's house. I used the chili garlic sauce instead of the red pepper flakes. Instead of serving the sauce on the side, I brushed it directly on the chicken after I turned them over the first time. I also broiled them longer than the recipe so they were crisp and not greasy. They were good, but they did not knock my socks off.

